    <note>Hong(1) Jiarui [17537] He was the first Chunan Hong(1) jinshi and I am identifying him as Zi(2)'s [17536] uncle, which would account for the sequence of correct generational names of Chunan Hong(1), which are not chronologically synchronous with the descendants of Zi(2). I would also explain why Zi(2)'s grandson, Shiqian [17540], held public office without earning the jinshi, highly unusual unless a kin of a previous generation had earned the degree. Zhejiang TZ, 125.11b.</note>
